content: I like the idea of allocating time for personal goals and self-care activities. For my personal goal, I want to focus on planning a project I've been putting off for weeks. Can you suggest a specific time slot each day for that? Also, I want to prioritize yoga classes on Tuesdays and Thursdays, and a 30-minute walk during my lunch break on Wednesdays. Can you fit those into the schedule as well?
